---
title: Italian-Seasoned Double Salmon with Baked Orzo
description: This light and delicious meal spotlights Italian-seasoned salmon, but the accompanying side could steal the show: creamy orzo is topped with zucchini and Parmesan and baked to dreamy perfection.
